NEWS:
A simple new system that allows for new messages. News items can be grouped using a tag if needed.
TAGS:
news
    'template' template to be used for showing the news, default is 'news.tpl'
        String, optional
    'tag'
        String, optional
    'max' maximum amount of news post to be displayed
        Int, optional
    'news_user' all posts showing the user with the given user id 
        Int, optional
newsitem, show the news item, the ID must be passed through the GET variable
newstags, show all tags used and the last post of it